$ MS Office: Trusted Locations

*Trusted Locations* is a → Microsoft/Office/security/Trust-Center list of directories on hard disks and locations on file shares where stored files are trusted.

The list of trusted locations is maintained in the registry under
→ Windows/registry/tree/HKEY_CURRENT_USER/Software/Microsoft/Office/application_version/application_name/Security/Trusted-Documents/TrustRecords[`HKEY_CURRENT_USER/Software/Microsoft/Office/{version}/{name}/Security/Trusted Locations`] (for example
→ Windows/registry/tree/HKEY_CURRENT_USER/Software/Microsoft/Office/application_version/Excel/Security/Trusted-Locations[`HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Software\Microsoft\Office\16.0\Excel\Security\Trusted Locations`])
